{"id": "art-20297", "label": "Art. 20297", "title": "Art. 20297: Actele încheiate de mandant", "slug": "art-20297", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_155740144\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1067\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_155740144\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 2029<sup>7</sup>:\nActele încheiate de mandant </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_559804723\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1066\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_559804723\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Actele juridice încheiate de mandant anterior\nîncuviin&#355;&#259;rii mandatului de ocrotire pot fi anulate sau\nobliga&#355;iile care decurg din acestea pot fi reduse numai dac&#259; la data\ncând au fost încheiate lipsa discern&#259;mântului era notorie sau\ncunoscut&#259; de cealalt&#259; parte.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_97297178\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1065\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_97297178\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Actele juridice încheiate de mandant ulterior\nîncuviin&#355;&#259;rii mandatului &#351;i incompatibile cu clauzele acestuia\nnu pot fi anulate sau obliga&#355;iile care decurg din acestea nu pot fi reduse\ndecât dac&#259; acesta a suferit un prejudiciu.</span></p>"}